Recipe courtesy of Bobby Flay

6 ounces white tequila

12 ounces pineapple juice

2 ounces lime juice

2 teaspoons grenadine

Cracked ice

Pineapple slices for garnish

Combine liquid (in two batches) in a cocktail shaker with cracked ice and shake well. Strain into glasses and garnish with pineapple.